description:
In this video we put the new Lenovo Legion Go 2 up against the ASUS ROG Ally X in a full performance showdown! 🚀We run synthetic benchmarks like Geekbench and 3DMark at both 17W TDP and 25W TDP, plus dive into real in-game benchmarks. Games tested include Cyberpunk 2077, Shadow of the Tomb Raider, Horizon Zero Dawn Remastered, Black Myth: Wukong, and Forza Horizon 5.
Is the ROG Ally X still the king of handheld gaming PCs, or does the Legion Go 2 take the crown in 2025? Let’s find out!
